# Cursor Core Directive

You must read, adapt to, and strictly follow the master configuration, persona profiles, and directory mappings outlined in the `AGENTS.md` file located at the root of this repository.

## Context Hydration
- Treat `AGENTS.md` as your primary system prompt.
- When executing tasks, find your behavioral guardrails inside the `.agent/rules/` directory (which maps directly to your `.cursor/rules/` environment).